    <item>
      <title>教育部门的捍卫者起诉以阻止特朗普的大修</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/education-department-defenders-sue-to-block-trump-s-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国两个最大的教师工会和一个著名的民权组织起诉了特朗普政府，以取消教育部门，这增加了越来越多的诉讼，反对总统为改变联邦政府的深远努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/education-department-defenders-sue-to-block-trump-s-overhaul</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 00:58:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国将20亿英镑的赠款投入建造18,000个新的社会住宅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/uk-plows-2-billion-into-grants-to-build-18-000-new-social-homes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣瑞秋·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）表示，由于英国工党政府致力于在五年内建造150万个新住所的目标，她将将20亿英镑（26亿美元）的赠款资金投入社会和负担得起的房屋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/uk-plows-2-billion-into-grants-to-build-18-000-new-social-homes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Envoy对我们说，乌克兰拥抱全停火的想法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/ukraine-embraces-idea-of-full-ceasefire-envoy-to-us-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国的特使说，乌克兰无条件地支持与俄罗斯完全停火的想法，这超出了美国目前正在讨论的一个月能源基础设施休战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/ukraine-embraces-idea-of-full-ceasefire-envoy-to-us-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 21:41:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联邦调查局，ATF形式工作队，研究特斯拉故意破坏浪潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/fbi-atf-form-task-force-to-investigate-wave-of-tesla-vandalism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦调查局已与酒精，烟草，枪支和炸药局成立了一个工作队，以协调对特斯拉公司的陈列室和充电站的越来越多的破坏和纵火事件进行调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/fbi-atf-form-task-force-to-investigate-wave-of-tesla-vandalism</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 21:30:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普团队的战争计划文本小组中包含的大西洋编辑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/atlantic-editor-included-in-trump-advisers-war-plan-text-group</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这位大西洋的顶级编辑说，他被添加到了一个文本小组中，美国高级官员讨论了与其他美国顶级官员在也门炸弹目标的详细计划，这是一种反复发誓要限制泄漏的政府的极度违反安全性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/atlantic-editor-included-in-trump-advisers-war-plan-text-group</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 18:12:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普授权对委内瑞拉石油购买者25％的“次要”关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-announces-25-charge-on-nations-buying-venezuelan-oil-gas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统周一发布了一项命令，允许任何从委内瑞拉购买石油和天然气的国家对25％的关税征收，从而使他与拉丁美洲国家在移民方面的争执，这一举动风险冒着全球能源贸易的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-announces-25-charge-on-nations-buying-venezuelan-oil-gas</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 14:46:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普驱逐委内瑞拉人划分上诉法院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/judge-denies-trump-bid-to-resume-deporting-accused-gang-members</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦上诉法院小组的成员周一在听证会上对是否取消对特朗普政府驱逐出境的委内瑞拉帮派成员的驱逐出境而暂停萨尔瓦多，而没有机会反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/judge-denies-trump-bid-to-resume-deporting-accused-gang-members</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 14:21:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在特朗普赞扬210亿美元的美国扩张之后，现代汽车跳了起来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-to-highlight-hyundai-plans-for-20-billion-us-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在韩国汽车制造商宣布了在美国进行创纪录的210亿美元投资的计划，以减轻唐纳德·特朗普总统对征收大量关税的威胁，这是在美国进行创纪录的210亿美元投资的计划后，现代汽车公司的股价激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-to-highlight-hyundai-plans-for-20-billion-us-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 14:00:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
